3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the proposed framework uses machine learning techniques to predict instance-aware keypoints.
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with processing images to estimate human poses.
5. cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible category as the proposed framework can be useful for robotics applications that require human pose estimation.
